再完美系統 最容易出問題關鍵地方 永遠都係人<br />\n允許用家關閉UAC就係第一個錯誤 <br />\n第二個錯誤係一般用家根本唔識分辨病毒偽裝普通程式執行 UAC含糊地描述程式想要做咩 完全冇寫清楚<br />\n第三個錯誤就係 UAC日日夜夜彈出黎 咩都問一餐 令用家產生煩厭同疲勞 <br />\n所以User通常連細節都唔睇 直接就按&quot;允許&quot; <br />\n以上三個錯誤先係導致windows成日中毒原因 <br />\n<br />\n可以自己透過bug繞過UAC 然後再用BUG提升權限到管理員權限執行攻擊既病毒根本少之又少 <br />\n大部分都係透過欺騙用戶點擊&quot;允許執行&quot;授權從而獲得攻擊系統權限<br />\n<br />\nMac個設計就係防止呢種情況發生 無論用戶授權程式做咩<br />\n都唔會係最高權限 最高權限永遠收埋OS核心 <br />\n所以就算係腦殘User咩都允許一餐 都唔會比程式入到系統核心<br />\n防止病毒用最高權限執行程式代碼"},{"pid":"6375eeb62c47180a72f2560e2be5f1e871464dae","tid":1948569,"uid":336645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T15:10:47.000Z","msg":"Mac都唔貴"},{"pid":"564e200d4d49bcfdc5e3281bf9658477b56d8b51","tid":1948569,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"sudo rm -rf /<br />\nmac係Terminal 用咗之後打機快過2080Ti<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbed5d1d27616854b305e12f843c5cd980ed6842","tid":1948569,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"564e200d4d49bcfdc5e3281bf9658477b56d8b51","tid":1948569,"uid":135475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T16:08:50.000Z","msg":"sudo rm -rf /<br />\nmac係Terminal 用咗之後打機快過2080Ti<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T19:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7642650d8800d9d2f1bc72f1e670e33e494d5b","tid":1948569,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0d3cef0d7d8159cf63043aebc5cfa451d8182a89","tid":1948569,"uid":196924,"like":56,"dislike":1,"score":55,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T06:14:33.000Z","msg":"當全世界都用Mac<br />\n啲games自然出晒Mac version<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2